Loop Same Ingredient for Condition and Decrement.

This recipe uses the same ingredient as both loop condition and decrement variable.

Ingredients.
3 g counter
49 g base

Method.
Beat the counter.
Put counter into mixing bowl.
Add base to mixing bowl.
Beat the counter until beaten.
Liquefy contents of the mixing bowl.
Pour contents of the mixing bowl into the baking dish.

Serves 1.
